<note n="0820035" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820035">觀＝樓【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0820036" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820036">語＝言【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0820037" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820037">怒＋（便）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0820038" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820038">〔乞〕－【宮】</note>
<note n="0820039" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820039">門監大恐怖＝監門人大懅【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0820040" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820040">牽＝掣【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0820041" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820041">撲＝撥【宮】</note>
<note n="0820042" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820042">折＋（其）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0820043" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820043">其＝於【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0820044" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820044">兒＋（呌）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0820045" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820045">〔言〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0820046" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820046">兩＝其【宮】</note>
<note n="0820047" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820047">〔等〕－【宮】</note>
<note n="0820048" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820048">乃取如是＝而取之爾【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0820049" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820049">到＝至【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0820050" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820050">牽撲傷我身＝掣撲折傷我【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0820051" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820051">〔便〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0820052" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820052">施＋（今）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0820053" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820053">也＝耳【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0820054" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820054">乃＝迺【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0820055" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820055">時＝如是【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0820056" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820056">〔分衛〕－【宮】</note>
<note n="0820057" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820057">佛＝遙見之便【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0820058" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820058">怱怱乃＝迺【宮】</note>
<note n="0820059" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820059">〔便〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0820060" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820060">盲＋（兒）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0820061" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820061">事＝末【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0820062" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820062">矜＝憐【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0820063" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0820063">創＝瘡【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0821001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0821001">〔折〕－【宮】</note>
<note n="0821002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0821002">（越）＋難【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0821003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0821003">〔懃苦〕－【宮】</note>
<note n="0821004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0821004">（爾時…意）九字＝佛故說偈言【三】，佛便說偈言【宮】</note>
<note n="0821005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0821005">（人求…果）四句二十字∞（有身…常）六句三十字【宮】</note>
<note n="0821006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0821006">（人求…果）四句二十字∞（有身…常）六句三十字【宮】</note>
<note n="0821007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0821007">暑＝熱【宮】</note>
<note n="0821008" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0821008">〔經〕－【宮】</note>
